    title: "Automation blocks with missing crednetials"
    description: "<p>The credentials feature is not working the exact problem is detailed here:</p>
                  <p><a target='_blank' href='https://monday-help.dsapps.dev/microsoft-365-office-embedded/missing-credentials'>
                  monday-help.dsapps.dev/microsoft-365-office-embedded/missing-credentials
